Author: Six_FoxSox
Text: I was at my GP today and because I’ve not noticed much weight change, they don’t think it’s much of an issue...

Author: petaldust
Text: see if your GP can refer you to a therapist specializing in eating disorders. your verbage does suggest to me that your eating habits are disordered, but i'm not a licensed health professional and can't give a diagnosis on whether that is due to your medication or an underlying issue. good luck. :)
